# New Horizons
Welcome! New Horizons is a textboard for Gemini written in Go.
To set your name, set the common name of the issuer of your certificate to the name you want.
Note that the names are not checked for uniqueness, and a hash of the public key and the public key itself are provided for identity.
You might not be able to enter the site without a client certificate.
Posts are UNABLE TO BE DELETED. Only the administrator can delete posts.

